RE Oct Estimate Revision JML Oil Cc Thanks Ill make the adjustments Kelly M Loocke Enron North America pager Original Message From Singer John Sent Friday October AM To Loocke Kelly Cc Mary Theresa NRON Hodge John Subject Oct Estimate Revision JML Oil Kelly I received a Revision in Estimates of Monthly Metered Supplies from CNR for JML Oil Gas for the month of October The original estimate was Dth on Contract Sitata per the CNR Oct Estimates supplied by Terry Franklin This volume should be reduced to per the revision faxed to me by Cath Clark However I would make the change effective next Tuesday for the balance of the month with cash price stron for the weekend Please call if you have questions John
